### Test Date Range Bulk Creation
### Login first to get token
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@tiffin.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Save the accessToken from response above, then use it below

### 1. Create meals using DATE RANGE (NEW FEATURE)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-19",
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Week lunch using date range"
}

### 2. Create meals using ARRAY (EXISTING FEATURE - Still works!)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "dates": ["2024-01-22", "2024-01-23", "2024-01-24"],
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 2,
  "note": "Specific dates dinner"
}

### 3. Create entire month of breakfasts
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-02-01",
  "endDate": "2024-02-29",
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "February breakfasts"
}

### 4. List meals in date range
GET http://localhost:3003/meals?startDate=2024-01-15&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get dashboard to see totals
GET http://localhost:3003/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
